# Observability Conventions

## Metrics naming
Use prefix:
signal_lab_

Examples:
- signal_lab_scenario_runs_total
- signal_lab_scenario_duration_seconds
- signal_lab_errors_total

## Logs format (JSON only)
{
  "app": "signal-lab",
  "scenarioType": "...",
  "scenarioId": "...",
  "level": "info|warn|error",
  "durationMs": 0
}

## Sentry rules
- Only system_error must create exception
- validation_error uses breadcrumb only
- Never send sensitive data